WEBVTT

00:12:28.186 --> 00:12:30.817
Pogledajmo ovu biljku.

00:12:30.817 --> 00:12:33.300
Centella asiatica. Korov je.

00:12:33.300 --> 00:12:35.448
Tako ga bar nazivamo.

00:12:35.448 --> 00:12:38.324
Ona raste u mnogim

00:12:38.324 --> 00:12:41.106
različitim staništima u Africi, u Aziji,

00:12:41.106 --> 00:12:43.125
Koristila se za

00:12:43.125 --> 00:12:45.892
za saniranje smrtonosne bolesti, lepre,

00:12:45.892 --> 00:12:50.338
na Madagaskaru
četrdesetih godina prošlog veka.

00:12:50.338 --> 00:12:53.868
Iako Centella raste širom sveta,

00:12:53.868 --> 00:12:57.159
u Africi, u Aziji,

00:12:57.159 --> 00:12:59.503
najbolja je ona sa Madagaskara,

00:12:59.503 --> 00:13:03.688
jer sadrži tri ključna sastojka